                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "This character can\u2019t tell if the tavern door is five feet or fifty feet away, leading to arrows that bury themselves in the ground or sail over rooftops. They squint at everything, misjudging distances with comical results\u2014like hugging a tree they thought was a person. Aiming at a moving target? Pure guesswork.",
